<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190368>
    bibo:endPage "55" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "39" ;
    bibo:volume "2234" ;
    dc:creator "Avila, Luciano Javier; Morando, Mariana; Perez, Daniel Roberto; Sites, Jack W." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Liolaemus from Añelo sand dunes, northern Patagonia, Neuquén, Argentina, and molecular phylogenetic relationships of the Liolaemus wiegmannii species group (Squamata, Iguania, Liolaemini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190369>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190370>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190371>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190372>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190373> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190369>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Liolaemus cuyumhue in life, lateral and ventral view of holotype (MACN 38981), adult male 51.2 mm in SVL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190369/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190370>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal and ventral color variation in the type series of Liolaemus cuyumhue (museum numbers are in diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190371>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Known distribution of wiegmannii species group. Large red star: type locality of Liolaemus cuyumhue. Red squares, L. azarai; orange squares: L. multimaculatus; green squares: L. salinicola; green circles: L. lutzae; yellow circles: L. scapularis; red circles: L. arambarensis; pink circles: L. occipitalis; blue circles: L. wiegmannii; black stars: L. riojanus; yellow square: L. rabinoi. Inset: satellite image of the Añelo basin, a red star mark the type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190371/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190372>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. General view of the type locality of Liolaemus cuyumhue." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190372/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190373>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Phylogenetic relationships of Liolaemus cuyumhue with other species of the wiegmannii group as shown by the consensus Bayesian tree. Posterior probabilities and maximum parsimony bootstrap values are shown above and below branches." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

